RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Suggests: 
    ggplot2 (>= 2.4.0),
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
LinkingTo: 
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.9)
Imports: 
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.9)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
